{"id":348229,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/05/翻墙-传新疆和田将临时管制微信和qq/","date":"2014-05-27T16:41:13Z","modified":"2014-05-27T21:35:02Z","title":"南华早报 |  新疆和田地区传将临时封锁微信QQ","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/Bon81w7IAAAyO7C.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-348206\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/Bon81w7IAAAyO7C.jpg\" alt=\"Bon81w7IAAAyO7C\" width=\"413\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/Bon81w7IAAAyO7C.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/Bon81w7IAAAyO7C-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 413px) 100vw, 413px\" /></a>《南华早报》<a href=\"http://www.nanzao.com/sc/china/28310/xin-jiang-he-tian-di-qu-chuan-jiang-lin-shi-feng-suo-wei-xin-qq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">报道</a>，多名新疆网民今日在微博等社交网络上传照片并发贴称，新疆和田地区将从明日零时起，对即时通信工具微信和QQ进行临时管制，不过当地居民仍可正常上网。《关于对部分即时通讯工具临时管制的通告》称，为切断境内外“三股势力”勾联、宣传、造谣、煽动渠道，从明日起，在保障正常上网、通话、短信的情况下，对和田地区即时通信工具微信和QQ先行采取临时管制措施。通告同时表示，对陌陌、米聊、YY语音、啪啪、易信等17种即时通讯工具，将根据实际适时采取临时管制措施。</p>\n<p>http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=39708</p>\n</div>\n<div>翻墙技术博客<a href=\"http://www.chinagfw.org/2013/09/blog-post.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">订阅地址及社交帐号</a></div>\n","author":1005,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,18424],"tags":[15390,18820,24081,9503,19665]}